FUNCTIONS

devtools::source_gist("79211b737aae2cd3b7ec15d1643bcc3d")

filled.contour.tidy function to plot 2d contour surfaces tidyverse format. Wrapper of ggplot and ggisoband.

Arguments:

dat dataset

month variable name for month scale

year variable name for year scale

var attribute name

hline yintercept values passed on directly to geom_hline

palette palette name passed on directly to scale_fill_distiller

trans name of a scale transformation passed on directly to scale_fill_distiller

log1 wether var be transformed to log10

dire direction of scale passed on directly to scale_fill_distiller

PLOTS

#devtools::install_github("clauswilke/ggisoband")
library(ggisoband)

a <- filled.contour.tidy(dt_region, month, year, pv, palette = "RdGy", dire = -1, hline = c(2006,2011))
b <- filled.contour.tidy(dt_region, month, year, pf, "RdGy", dire = -1, hline = c(2006,2011))

library(gridExtra)
grid.arrange(a,b, nrow = 1, ncol=2)
